Uses of Package
org.terrier.matching.models.aftereffect

Packages that use org.terrier.matching.models.aftereffect
org.terrier.matching.models Provides the classes that implement various classical IR models, as well as models from the Divergence From Randomness (DFR) framework. 
org.terrier.matching.models.aftereffect Provides the interface and the classes for implementing the term frequency normalisation component in the DFR framework. 
 

Classes in org.terrier.matching.models.aftereffect used by org.terrier.matching.models
AfterEffect
          This class provides a contract for implementing the first normalisation by after effect models for the DFR framework.
